#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:116
msgid ""
"The presence of Master Perrin's journeymen gives you the ability to recruit "
"mages."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:126
msgid ""
"We should be on the outskirts of the settled country around Kal Kartha, but "
"something doesn't feel right here."
msgstr "我们该在Kal Kartha领土的边境了，但这里感觉不大对劲。"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:130
msgid "It's too quiet...and I think I smell traces of smoke on the wind."
msgstr "太安静了...我想我闻到风中的烟味。"

#. [message]: speaker=Ratheln
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:134
msgid ""
"I do not sense hostile magic in the vicinity.  But there has been fire near "
"here recently, and not a clean one."
msgstr ""
"我没感觉到附近有敌对的魔法力量。 但这里附近刚刚烧过，而且不是干净的焚烧。"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:138
msgid ""
"Look sharp for the inhabitants here.  They might have something to tell us."
msgstr "仔细寻找这里的居民。他们可能会告诉我们点什么。"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:145
msgid "Find the inhabitants"
msgstr "寻找居民"

#. [unit]: type=Peasant, description=Ollin
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:184
#, fuzzy
msgid "Ollin"
msgstr "Ollin"

#. [message]: speaker=Ollin
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:192
msgid "Don't kill me, masters!  Please don't kill me!"
msgstr "别杀我，主人！求你别杀我！"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:196
msgid "You're in no danger from us.  What lies to the east of here?"
msgstr "你在我们这就脱离危险了。这儿东边有什么吗？"

#. [message]: speaker=Ollin
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:200
msgid "You wear no mask.  You...you're not with them?"
msgstr "你们没带面具。你们...你们不是和他们一伙的？"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:204
msgid "What are you talking about?"
msgstr "你在说些什么？"

#. [message]: speaker=Ollin
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:208
msgid "The masked dwarves.  Killing, burning, kidnapping.  Look..."
msgstr "是面具矮人。杀戮，焚烧，诱骗。看..."

#. [message]: speaker=Masked Dwarf
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Fellow dwarves, hail!  We're looking for a human refugee, one named Ollin.  "
"Have you seen him?  Our master demands his life."
msgstr ""
"矮人朋友，嘿！我们在找一位人类难民，叫Ollin。你们看到他了吗？我们主人要他的"
"命。"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:234
msgid ""
"He is here.  How has he wronged your master, that you seek\n"
"his death?"
msgstr "他在这里。他对你们的主人犯了什么错，让你们要他死？"

#. [message]: speaker=Masked Dwarf
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:238
msgid ""
"Does it matter?  He is only a dirtgrubbing human, not fit to polish the "
"boots of the true people."
msgstr "这重要吗？他不过是个挖地的人，根本不配拥有良民的尊敬地位。"

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:243
msgid ""
"What is your name, masked one?  Will you stand behind your\n"
"deed?  I am a witness."
msgstr "你的名字是什么，带面具的？你是你们行为的指使？我是见证者。"

#. [message]: speaker=Masked Dwarf
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:247
msgid ""
"A witness?  My name is...my name is not important. My deed will speak its "
"own truth."
msgstr "见证者？我的名字是...我的名字并不重要。我的行为会说明它的正确性。"

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:251
msgid ""
"You speak without honor. Mine is the power of our ancient Law; speak your "
"name and give up your murder, or the Law will cast you forth.  I am a "
"witness!"
msgstr ""
"你说的太不礼貌了。我的权利来自古代法典。讲出你的名字并停止你的谋杀，不然法律"
"将驱逐你。我是见证者！"

#. [message]: speaker=Masked Dwarf
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:255
msgid ""
"If you were a witness of the true people, you would not let a dirtgrubber "
"hide behind your robes.  I deny you!"
msgstr ""
"如果你是良民的见证者，你就不会让这个挖地的躲在你的长袍后面了。我拒绝回答！"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:259
msgid "Up axes!"
msgstr "拿起斧头！"

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:263
msgid "The Law speaks: you are cast out.  You are un-dwarf.  I AM A WITNESS!"
msgstr "法典上说：你被驱逐了。你不是矮人了。我是见证者。"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:270
msgid "Defeat the Masked Dwarf"
msgstr "击败面具矮人"

#. [message]: description=Ollin
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:296
msgid "Take that for my family's memory, you murderer!"
msgstr "为了我家庭，接招，你这个凶手！"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:304
msgid "They are defeated"
msgstr "他们被击败了。"

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:308
msgid "You have acted in honor.  I am a witness."
msgstr "你做的光荣。我是见证者。"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:312
msgid ""
"I have never seen the formal banishment before.  One reads of it in the old "
"tales, of course, but to hear it with one's own ears? It was...unsettling."
msgstr ""
"我从来没见过正式的驱逐。只在老故事里读过，当然，亲耳听到这个？那真令人...不"
"安。"

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:316
msgid ""
"It is not something we do often.  The last such was in my grandsire's time.  "
"But look at what these filth were carrying if you have any doubt it was "
"merited."
msgstr ""
"那可不是我们经常做的。最后一次驱逐还是在我祖父时代呢。但如果你怀疑他们否是罪"
"有因得，你看着这些运送的污秽物品。"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:320
msgid ""
"Whips.  Shackles.  No, Angarthing, I would not doubt you, even if it were my "
"place to doubt a loremaster."
msgstr "鞭子。手铐。不，Angarthing，即使怀疑一位智慧大师，我也没怀疑你。"

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:324
msgid ""
"They were seeking captives.  To what purpose, I cannot say.  But I doubt it "
"was any good one."
msgstr "他们在找俘虏。为了什么目的，我没法回答。但我怀疑也不是好目的。"

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:3
msgid "Forbidden Forest"
msgstr "禁行森林"

#. [side]: type=Elvish High Lord, description=Telcherion
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:47
#, fuzzy
msgid "Telcherion"
